data.description: Fresh easy living in this fresh painted & new carpet home in the Pleasanton Farms Community. Enjoy two large blooming Texas Mountain Laurels bordering the drive way and beautiful rose bushes tracing the walkway to the front door. The open concept living, dining, and kitchen area with peninsula seating invites warm conversations and gatherings. The main level supports an optimally placed laundry room, making your routine chores a hassle-free experience. Downstairs features a secondary bedroom and full bathroom with stall shower perfect for hosting guests or setting up a quiet home office space. Split from the other rooms, the primary includes a walk-in closet, a double vanity and a stall shower. Backyard patio with gazebo overlooks intimate yard space for minimal upkeep but plenty of room for any type of little ones furry ones. The location is an absolute advantage with quick access to highway 410, and the convenience of being just minutes away from Texas A&M University and Palo Alto College. An abundance of shops, restaurants nearby uplift your living experience. The close proximity to the San Antonio Missions National Historical Park offers enriching weekend getaways.
